      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>transmutation  The Glutton is an intelligent +3 keen wounding longsword. The Glutton is a CE weapon with Int 13, Wis 13, Cha 13, Ego 11 and communicates by empathy (a driving hunger). It transmits touch attacks such as vampiric level drain as if it were an extension of its wielder's body. Any blood spilled upon the blade soaks into the sword like a sponge.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +3 keen wounding longsword</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, bleed, enervation, keen edge</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Rappan Athuk",
